      <title>比特币下滑 难以利用全球风险偏好反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bitcoin-s-btc-august-drop-leaves-token-lagging-global-market-revival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管全球股市在摆脱对美国经济增长的担忧后回升至历史高位，但比特币和更广泛的加密货币市场本月迄今仍在大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bitcoin-s-btc-august-drop-leaves-token-lagging-global-market-revival</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 07:41:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美将成立金融压力案例联络小组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/china-us-team-up-on-contact-group-to-handle-financial-stress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行表示，在上海举行的会议与美国财政部达成协议，任命联络人员应对未来的任何“金融压力事件”，这是世界两大经济体寻求共同点的罕见例子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/china-us-team-up-on-contact-group-to-handle-financial-stress</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:23:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
